'''Matías Galarza Fonda''' (born 11 February 2002) is a Paraguayan professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[midfielder]] for [[Major League Soccer]] club [[Atlanta United FC|Atlanta United]] on loan from Argentinian club [[Club Atlético River Plate|River Plate]] and the [[Paraguay national football team|Paraguay national team]].

==Club career==
Born in [[Asunción]], Galarza represented hometown side [[Club Olimpia|Olimpia]]. On 19 June 2020, he moved on loan to Brazilian club [[CR Vasco da Gama|Vasco da Gama]] until 2022, and was initially assigned to the under-20 squad.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.lance.com.br/vasco/anuncia-contratacao-jovem-meio-campista-paraguaio.html|title=Vasco anuncia a contratação de jovem meio-campista paraguaio|trans-title=Vasco announce the signing of young Paraguayan midfielder|publisher=[[Lance!]]|language=pt-BR|date=19 June 2020|accessdate=10 May 2021}}</ref>

After impressing with the under-20s, Galarza made his senior debut on 3 March 2021, after coming on as a half-time [[Substitute (association football)|substitute]] for [[Vinícius Paiva|Vinícius]] in a 0–1 [[Campeonato Carioca]] home loss against [[Associação Atlética Portuguesa (RJ)|Portuguesa]];<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.uol.com.br/esporte/futebol/ultimas-noticias/2021/03/03/vasco-x-portuguesa.htm|title=Com sub-20, Vasco estreia com derrota para Portuguesa no Carioca|trans-title=With under-20s, Vasco debut with defeat to Portuguesa in the Carioca|publisher=[[Universo Online|UOL Esporte]]|language=pt-BR|date=3 March 2021|accessdate=10 May 2021}}</ref> at the age of 19, he became the youngest foreigner to play for Vasco in the 21st century.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://vasco.com.br/matias-galarza-o-estrangeiro-mais-novo-a-atuar-pelo-vasco-no-seculo-21/|title=Matías Galarza, o estrangeiro mais novo a atuar pelo Vasco no Século 21|trans-title=Matías Galarza, the youngest foreigner to play for Vasco in the 21st century|publisher=CR Vasco da Gama|language=pt-BR|date=5 March 2021|accessdate=10 May 2021|archive-date=10 May 2021|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210510164837/https://vasco.com.br/matias-galarza-o-estrangeiro-mais-novo-a-atuar-pelo-vasco-no-seculo-21/|url-status=dead}}</ref> He scored his first goal as a professional on 24 March, netting his team's third in a 3–1 home success over [[Macaé Esporte Futebol Clube|Macaé]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.espn.com.br/futebol/artigo/_/id/8372670/carioca-galarza-faz-golaco-vasco-derrota-e-macae-e-vence-a-primeira-na-competicao |title=Carioca: Galarza faz golaço, Vasco derrota e Macaé e vence a primeira na competição|trans-title=Carioca: Galarza scores great goal, Vasco defeat Macaé and win the first one in the competition|publisher=[[ESPN Brasil]]|language=pt-BR|date=24 March 2021|accessdate=10 May 2021}}</ref>

On 20 May 2021, Galarza signed a permanent contract with Vasco until 2025,<ref>{{cite web|url=https://vasco.com.br/matias-galarza-e-do-vasco-da-gama/|title=Matías Galarza é do Vasco da Gama!|trans-title=Matías Galarza is of Vasco da Gama!|publisher=CR Vasco da Gama|language=pt-BR|date=20 May 2021|accessdate=20 May 2021|archive-date=20 May 2021|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210520190951/https://vasco.com.br/matias-galarza-e-do-vasco-da-gama/|url-status=dead}}</ref> after the club bought 60% of his economic rights for a fee of [[American dollar|US$]] 500,000.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://globoesporte.globo.com/futebol/times/vasco/noticia/vasco-anuncia-contratacao-do-meio-campista-matias-galarza.ghtml|title=Vasco anuncia compra dos direitos de Galarza|trans-title=Vasco announces the acquisition of Galarza's rights|publisher=GloboEsporte.com|language=pt-BR|date=20 May 2021|accessdate=20 May 2021}}</ref> A regular starter during the remainder of the campaign, he lost his starting spot in 2022.

On 4 April 2022, Galarza moved to [[Campeonato Brasileiro Série A|Série A]] side [[Coritiba Foot Ball Club|Coritiba]] on loan for the remainder of the year.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://coritiba.com.br/artigo/38702/seja_bem_vindo_matias_galarza|title=Seja bem-vindo, Matías Galarza|trans-title=Welcome, Matías Galarza|publisher=Coritiba FBC|language=pt-BR|date=4 April 2022|accessdate=10 April 2022}}</ref>

